data.title: Delta Sonic Car Wash
data.meta_description: For the ultimate comfort and convenience, get your car serviced at the Delta Sonic in Webster, NY. You can sit and wait in the Super Plus Club!
data.text:
Your car’s NEW best friend

The NEW Super Plus Club at Delta Sonic’s Webster, NY, location has everything your car needs. With self-serve vacuums, air for tires, glass cleaner, mat cleaners, windshield washer fluid, towels, and compressed air for cracks and crevices, your car will thank you.

Maintenance matters

Did you know our certified Delta Sonic technicians can help you maintain your vehicle for optimum performance and safety? Fluids, filters, belts, wiper blades, lights, AC, power steering, tire rotation, and engine tune-ups are all important factors in caring for your car. Check out our Maintenance by Mileage guidelines or review your operator’s manual for tips on when to get service.

I sincerely appreciate this Delta Sonic location because of employees like Amador. Everything is always clear and upfront. The work is efficient and thorough. I will continue to bring my car back here every single time because of the trust I have when he works on it. There is no other mechanic or tech I would rather go to in the Rochester area.
